<div i18n:domain="schooltool">
  <p i18n:translate="">
    SchoolTool is free administrative software for schools around the
    world.  The goals of the project are to create a simple turnkey
    student information system or managment information system for
    primary and secondary schools, as well as a framework for building
    customized applications and configurations for individual schools
    or states.
  </p>
  <p i18n:translate="">
    SchoolTool is built on a 100% open source software stack,
    written in <a href="http://python.org">Python</a> using the 
    <a href="http://zope.org">Zope 3</a> framework.
  </p>
  <p i18n:translate="">
